INSERT INTO `blogs` VALUES (1,'Can I receive channels if I\'m under trees.','can-i-receive-channels-if-im-under-trees',NULL,1,NULL,1,10,'2021-09-03 18:40:08','2021-09-03 18:40:08','<div class=\"container mb-5\">\r\n<div class=\"row\">\r\n<div class=\"col-sm-12\">\r\n<div class=\"card mb-3\">\r\n<div class=\"card-header well-faq fz-13\">\r\n<div id=\"catfaq_62191\">\r\n<div class=\"card-body\">\r\n<p>If the trees are in the north or nor nor east direction (when you are in the eastern states) or north east (in WA) you may not be able to get channels, try moving your van a few metres and try to search again.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"container mb-5\">\r\n<div class=\"row\">\r\n<div class=\"col-sm-12\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>'),(2,'New SBS Channel on VAST','new-sbs-channel-on-vast',NULL,0,'2019-07-01',1,20,'2021-09-03 18:52:17','2021-09-03 18:52:17','<p>The SBS network have added a new channel to their VAST channel line-up today &ldquo;SBS World Movies&rdquo; on channel 32 this service is in High Definition. Also SBS 1 has now been changed from an SD service to a HD service now called &ldquo;SBS HD&rdquo; this channel remains on channel 3. There is no need for you to make any changes to your VAST decoders as this change will be updated automatically.</p>'),(3,'Satking Orbit publish in Time to Roam','satking-orbit-publish-in-time-to-roam',NULL,0,'2019-08-13',1,30,'2021-09-03 18:53:59','2021-09-03 18:53:59','<p>Satking Orbit Fully Automatic Satellite TV System is publish&nbsp; in the magazine - Time to Roam- issue 40, PG 41</p>\r\n<p><img src=\"/photos/1/news/ROAM33_FP_Orbit_&fnof;.jpeg\" alt=\"\" width=\"2835\" height=\"3872\" /></p>'),(4,'Melbourne Stage 4 Lockdown','melbourne-stage-4-lockdown',NULL,0,'2020-08-05',1,40,'2021-09-03 18:57:25','2021-09-03 18:57:25','<p>The Victorian Government has announced stage 4 lockdown for 11:59pm Wednesday 5/08/2020. Phoenix Technology Group will continue to operate at a reduced capacity under the new restrictions announced but as more information comes available this may change, we will advise of any changes to our operations as soon as we are aware. There will also be some changes to our current operations as we will have to operate under a new Covid Safe Plan during this time.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Retail sales will now be totally on-line during the stage 4 lockdown, couriers are still running so orders will be processed and delivered. The shopfront will close at 5pm on Wednesday the 5/08/2020</li>\r\n<li>Trade counter on-site sales will be contactless only via click and collect, this means you will need to phone/online order at least 30 minutes ahead to place and pay for your order over the phone/online. No cash payments will be permitted. When the order is ready it will be placed outside the #1 roller door under cover, there will be strictly no contact. For any trade warranty related issues call ahead to discuss as no on-site contact will be permitted.</li>\r\n<li>Online/Email orders will continue to be processed and dispatched but with reduced staff levels to meet the new government requirements. This will mean there will be some delays in order processing so please allow some extra time. Couriers are still running.</li>\r\n<li>Phone Technical support will also be impacted during this time due to reduced staff numbers, technical support will still be provided but longer than usual wait times would be expected.</li>\r\n</ul>'),(5,'Public Holiday Notice','public-holiday-notice',NULL,0,'2020-08-16',1,50,'2021-09-03 18:58:19','2021-09-03 18:58:19','<p>Our office will be closed on the Friday the 23rd of October 2020 for the AFL Grand Final Public Holiday. The office will re-open on Monday the 26th of October at 9AM.</p>'),(6,'Office Closure 23/12/2020','office-closure-23122020',NULL,0,'2020-12-23',1,60,'2021-09-03 19:04:28','2021-09-03 19:04:28','<p>Note we are now on Xmas holidays and the office will be closed from 5pm the 23rd of December 2020 and re-open at 9am on the 6th of January. We would like to wish all of our customer and dealers and merry Xmas and a happy new year.</p>'),(7,'VAST Channel Changes','vast-channel-changes',NULL,0,'2021-07-01',1,70,'2021-09-03 19:05:14','2021-09-03 19:05:14','<p>There were some major changes to the channel names and positions on the VAST platform last night.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>In WA, Win TV and Nine services were swapped around and the channel names and some channel numbers have changed. There is still possibly another channel change coming shortly, we will advise when this happens.</p>\r\n<p>In the eastern states there has been some changes to the news channel names and content to reflect recent mergers in regional news rooms.</p>\r\n<p>These channel lists are updated dynamically from the broadcasters so there is no need to doing anything.</p>'),(9,'Satking-Promax-Caravan-Satellite-Dish','satking-promax-caravan-satellite-dish','/photos/1/blogs/Satking-Promax-Product-Image.jpeg',2,'2019-04-03',1,90,'2021-09-03 19:20:22','2021-09-03 19:45:57','<p><strong>Watch Tv From Anywhere In Australia. </strong></p>\r\n<p>- Best Caravan Satellite Dish</p>\r\n<p>- Fully automatic self-aligning.</p>\r\n<p>- Australia Wide Coverage</p>\r\n<p>- Connects within 80 Secs.</p>\r\n<p>- VAST and Foxtel Pre-Programmed</p>\r\n<p>- Flat panel design offers compact size.</p>\r\n<p>- Dual output LNB as standard.</p>\r\n<p>- Built-in 24 Channel GPS to find satellites fast</p>\r\n<p>- Not affected by wind like the large round dishes.</p>\r\n<p>- Suitable for Caravan, motorhome, motor vehicle.</p>\r\n<p>- Automatic retraction when you exceed 10KPH.</p>\r\n<p>- Automatic LNB skew.</p>\r\n<p>- Powerful DC motors with metal gears.</p>\r\n<p>- Can be self-installed.</p>\r\n<p>- Detailed instructions and roof mount included.</p>\r\n<p>- 3 Year warranty.</p>\r\n<p>- 1300 Number helpline (no answering machine)</p>\r\n<p>- Made for harsh Australian conditions.</p>\r\n<p>- Requires less roof area than conventional dish.</p>\r\n<p>- Aussie Owned.</p>\r\n<p>Price - $3,495</p>\r\n<p><img src=\"/photos/1/blogs/Satking-Promax-Product-Image.jpeg\" alt=\"\" width=\"602\" height=\"602\" /></p>\r\n<p>Learn More -</p>\r\n<p><a href=\"https://l.facebook.com/l.php?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.satkingpromax.com.au%2F%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR25Br94MfX2v6LDjVt431Zy6izoTdrctShMc9A9bh86xBNS586EA5Jx28E&amp;h=AT3x6ccDl9i2Y82oVa1giy8UcSn5wls8ZGZzBwTuKhD-jF8Mu8cQzaNCVtRmCuooA0qMKSyuB73tKesVK7mP_77xqiJOl9U7WkjYnrz1MLbDZGFYDm22OIQvn5d1V7s8hUmgcktPNelk2bNWmcKg2h5d0zLO0iYi5xyUwC-9sUcAxVWpvmDMGOeDVt_HbVSQno_1DCKQ-MpEy5ACiIYg5zxJlJiFnbEkkKxrRL7hDkCO6xs9l70NVn-yBJRWBoBhf9QCDaq2JRo7Ra9n9Zrl-IWSuYn-HSin638CI6UYb90i4xSUYKo4iZN0oX2KOFOn72QPfnp-EDB7P1VUTLNAup9iTTSa-Uvc76_Lq1c2StLgK9jm2550eJgOYDKK3Ajk2uG7qVYKhtjUn44ZP0lOygcS4sQ076ZUaZIDR1WSEJAvauH8ASiUdZNgsti-6YR43CMMq0La8b8XVKU9sb6Ty3_YcTtqHqLeUhYzCamdvbFtep_Xx83E6z0HwAPnrCSZBldY6EywTe7oA9idGgjjlD9QylTeZQIHY7FLs2AhP3weJvdrwKafA0rZJQfsEo7ymX_nGocd7xWUVGz7FNjDRllerWZxNSKMXd5MLJ3AfJNzhA6SGOtfE0vSTOTU_RyZ6AKeJRHLpGMH6B5u9hyhUTc\">http://www.satkingpromax.com.au/</a></p>\r\n<p>Check your Local dealer -</p>\r\n<p><a href=\"http://www.satkingpromax.com.au/product/where-to-buy.htm?fbclid=IwAR2GHUMc7bqbLf8gXcZOl5jya3mZ08YN9Vly9Y0VdCLgCRbQKWxEzuDMZPQ\">http://www.satkingpromax.com.au/product/where-to-buy.htm</a></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>'),(10,'Satking Orbit Vs Satking Promax','satking-orbit-vs-satking-promax','/photos/1/blogs/Satking Orbit vs Satking Promax.jpeg',2,'2019-05-26',1,100,'2021-09-03 19:20:22','2021-09-03 19:59:05','<p><strong>Satking orbit vs Satking ProMax</strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Satking is the leading manufacturer of fully automated satellite dishes for caravans and motorhomes in the Australian market and running from 21 years. Satking is owned and run by a Australian, which has suppliers all over Australia. Everyone can get ease to enjoy the fully automatic Dishes to watch TV on the go. The entire system contains two most prominent and different products Satking orbit &amp; Satking ProMax. Let&rsquo;s have a look at each of these to know which can be better to avail.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h1><img src=\"/photos/1/blogs/Satking-Orbit-Vs-Satking-Promax.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"359\" height=\"538\" /></h1>\r\n<h1>&nbsp;</h1>\r\n<h1>Satking orbit</h1>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Satking Orbit is a perfect Caravan Satellite Dish which is meant to provide better services for the motorhome and caravan users in a cost effective way.&nbsp; This is a perfect Satellite dish for the caravan which comes with a dish reflector of 85cm and its metal gear system can ensure its reliability for years of operation.</p>\r\n<h1>Key Features&nbsp;</h1>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>1.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Wide coverage:</strong> it has an 85cm high gain dish which has the ability to provide wider coverage with ease for Foxtel and VAST&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>2.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Fast to find the satellite service:</strong> A built-in GPS system will help to locate your position and Satking will locate the exact satellite accordingly and let you connect the system within 80 seconds.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>3.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Perfectly designed to survive in the harsh Australian weather</strong>: A perfect dish option for the people of Australia to have. Its metal gears and the rugged system will make it easier for it to survive in harsh conditions.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>4.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Warranty and support:</strong> It comes with 2 years of warranty and full support from Satking which is a well-known Australian company.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>5.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Easy to use:</strong> The system is entirely automatic. To get started you just have to push the OK button.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>6.&nbsp;</strong>&nbsp;&nbsp; <strong>Best Value for money</strong>: Satking Orbit is priced at $2,195 which is much cheaper than ProMax and other Fully Automatic Caravan satellite dishes. Even though it is cheaper in price but it works the same as the other dishes and has fully automatic features, Foxtel, HD and dual LNB.&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h1>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; <img src=\"/photos/1/blogs/Satking-Promax-Vs-Satking-Orbit-Satellite-Dish.jpeg\" alt=\"\" width=\"363\" height=\"543\" /></h1>\r\n<h1>Satking Promax</h1>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">The Satking ProMax is a completely automatic motorized and most advanced dish TV system of Australia, which comes with a flat panel. This system suits perfectly for the VAST and Foxtel satellite TV. Its unit comes with dual LNB outputs which can serve the best to the twin tuner STBs with ease. It is a simple to use option which provides the best opportunity to enjoy the TV transmissions on the go.</p>\r\n<h1>Key features of Satking ProMax</h1>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>1.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Big performance</strong>: Flat panel of the dish system provides more coverage and has the ability to offer a compact size. This can be perfect to get the best performance with ease.&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>2.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Reduced search time:</strong> It keeps your previous memories save which will help you to get started from where you left the process. This is an amazing feature which will save your search time with ease.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>3.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Warranty and support</strong>: It comes with 3 years warranty and 1300 number support line. A perfect dish TV which is meant to survive in the harsh Australian condition with ease.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>4.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Reliability: </strong>It comes with metal gears and a powerful DC motor which ensure its long life perfectly.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>5.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Easy to use:</strong> Small footprints of the system makes it entirely easy to install. You can install it by yourself with ease because it comes with roof mounting kit and Detailed Instructions. You will also get features like Foxtel, Dual LNB, HD compatible, Built-in GPS and Fully Motorized. &nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>6.</strong>&nbsp; <strong>Advanced Technology</strong>: This is one of the most advanced caravan satellite systems, which you can find in Australia to get connected to the digital shows with ease. In fact, there are no other dishes available in Australia with similar technology.&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h5>Verdict</h5>\r\n<p>You can never complain about TV reception anymore. It is because Satking orbit &amp; Satking ProMax have arrived in the Australia market as the best caravan satellite system. Satking orbit &amp; Satking ProMax are meant to provide you the perfect reception of entire free to air, digital channels and Foxtel in the best possible way.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">For more visit -</p>\r\n<p><a href=\"https://www.satkingorbit.com.au/\">https://www.satkingorbit.com.au/</a></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><!--EndFragment--></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">&nbsp;</p>'),(11,'What Is Caravan Satellite Dish?','what-is-caravan-satellite-dish','photos/1/blogs/Satking-Orbit-Sat-Dish-For-Caravan.jpeg',2,'2019-06-24',1,110,'2021-09-03 19:20:22','2021-09-03 19:56:47','<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h1 class=\"MsoTitle\">Caravan Satellite Dish</h1>\r\n<!-- [if gte mso 9]><xml>\r\n <o:DocumentProperties>\r\n  <o:Revision>0</o:Revision>\r\n  <o:TotalTime>0</o:TotalTime>\r\n  <o:Pages>1</o:Pages>\r\n  <o:Words>71</o:Words>\r\n  <o:Characters>408</o:Characters>\r\n  <o:Lines>3</o:Lines>\r\n  <o:Paragraphs>1</o:Paragraphs>\r\n  <o:CharactersWithSpaces>478</o:CharactersWithSpaces>\