INSERT INTO `product` VALUES (1,'Satking Orbit Fully Automatic Satellite TV System','5573','satking-orbit-fully-automatic-satellite-tv-system','$2195.00','http://satkingorbit.test/photos/1/main/Caravan-Satellite-Dish.jpeg','null',0,'[\"http:\\/\\/satkingorbit.test\\/photos\\/1\\/main\\/Caravan-Satellite-Dish.jpeg\",\"http:\\/\\/satkingorbit.test\\/photos\\/1\\/main\\/Caravan-TV-Aerial.jpeg\",\"http:\\/\\/satkingorbit.test\\/photos\\/1\\/main\\/Best-Satellite-Dish-For-Caravans.jpeg\",\"http:\\/\\/satkingorbit.test\\/photos\\/1\\/main\\/Caravan-Satellite-Dish-For-Sale.jpeg\",\"http:\\/\\/satkingorbit.test\\/photos\\/1\\/main\\/Best-Caravan-Satellite-System.jpeg\",\"http:\\/\\/satkingorbit.test\\/photos\\/1\\/main\\/Caravan-TV-Antenna.jpeg\"]',NULL,'<p>Want to use a Satking Orbit on a truck or a bus? Then you will need this 24VDC to 12VDC downconverter. The Orbit just runs on voltages up to 15VDC but some vehicles are configured for 24VDC, if this is the case you will require this device. The unit connect between the power cables of the Orbit and you vehicles power system. Make sure you have at least 5AMPs available in you power system.</p>','<p>The Orbit has a 85CM high gain dish to provide coverage for VAST &amp; Foxtel Australia wide. Just press OK, simple.</p>\r\n<p>Utilising the latest in GPS technology to locate your exact location, the Orbit will quickly locate the desired satellite signal.</p>\r\n<p>The SatKing Orbit is built for harsh Australian conditions, it&rsquo;s rugged, well made with all metal drive gears. Designed in Australia and produced in Korea, the unit is perfect for travelling off the beaten track.</p>\r\n<p>The Orbit represents great value for money and is big on features but low on cost.</p>\r\n<p>The SatKing Orbit is backed with a 2 year Australian warranty and fully supported by SatKing, a big Australian-owned company. Need assistance or help whilst on the road? Don&rsquo;t worry, we have a 1300 helpline to assist you on your travels.</p>','<ul>\r\n<li>85cm High Gain Dish</li>\r\n<li>VAST &amp; Foxtel Compatible</li>\r\n<li>Fully Automatic Self Aligning</li>\r\n<li>Easy to Use</li>\r\n<li>Built in 24CH GPS to Find Satellites Fast</li>\r\n<li>Australia-Wide Coverage</li>\r\n<li>2 Year Warranty</li>\r\n<li>Dual Output LNB as Standard to Suit Twin Tuner STB&rsquo;s</li>\r\n<li>Suits both Caravans and Motorhomes</li>\r\n<li>Automatic LNB Skew</li>\r\n<li>Powerful DC Motors with Metal Gearing</li>\r\n<li>Weatherproof Construction</li>\r\n<li>Made for Harsh Australian Conditions</li>\r\n<li>MPEG4 HD Compatible</li>\r\n<li>Easy Installation</li>\r\n<li>1300 Number Help Line</li>\r\n<li>Designed in Australia</li>\r\n<li>Made in Korea</li>\r\n</ul>','<h2>Physical Specifications</h2>\r\n<ul class=\"time-list \">\r\n<li class=\"time-item \">\r\n<div class=\"name\">Dish Dimensions</div>\r\n<div class=\"date\">86.0 w x 91.0L cm</div>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"time-item  \">\r\n<div class=\"name\">Physical Dimensions</div>\r\n<div class=\"date\">110.6(L) x 86.0(W) x 18.4(H) cm / 15.1 kg</div>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"time-item  \">\r\n<div class=\"name\">Controller Dimensions</div>\r\n<div class=\"date\">199.0(w) x 154.0(d) x 31.0(h) mm</div>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"time-item  \">\r\n<div class=\"name\">Product Weight</div>\r\n<div class=\"date \">13.8kgs</div>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"time-item  \">\r\n<div class=\"name\">Gift Box Weight</div>\r\n<div class=\"date\">15.1kgs</div>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"time-item  \">\r\n<div class=\"name\">Operating Temperature Range</div>\r\n<div class=\"date\">-20&deg;C ~ +60&deg;C</div>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h2>LNB</h2>\r\n<ul class=\"time-list \">\r\n<li class=\"time-item \">\r\n<div class=\"name\">Polarization</div>\r\n<div class=\"date\">Horizontal/vertical</div>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"time-item  \">\r\n<div class=\"name\">Dual Output Wideband</div>\r\n<div class=\"date\">Dual Output</div>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"time-item \">\r\n<div class=\"name\">LNB Input Frequency</div>\r\n<div class=\"date \">11.75-12.75GHz</div>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"time-item  \">\r\n<div class=\"name\">LNB Output Frequency</div>\r\n<div class=\"date\">1000 - 2050 MHz</div>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h2>Antenna Adjustment Range</h2>\r\n<ul class=\"time-list \">\r\n<li class=\"time-item  \">\r\n<div class=\"name\">Elevation</div>\r\n<div class=\"date\">0&deg;-145&deg;</div>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"time-item  \">\r\n<div class=\"name\">Azimuth</div>\r\n<div class=\"date\">390&deg;</div>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"time-item  \">\r\n<div class=\"name\">Skew</div>\r\n<div class=\"date\">-60&deg; ~+60&deg;</div>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h2>Satellite Searching Time</h2>\r\n<ul class=\"time-list \">\r\n<li class=\"time-item  \">\r\n<div class=\"name\">Searching Time</div>\r\n<div class=\"date\">80 Seconds(Average)</div>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h2>Power</h2>\r\n<ul class=\"time-list \">\r\n<li class=\"time-item  \">\r\n<div class=\"name\">Input Voltage</div>\r\n<div class=\"date\">DC 12 voltage range 10.5-16V</div>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"time-item  \">\r\n<div class=\"name\">Consumption</div>\r\n<div class=\"date\">60 Watts in Search Mode - 4W Standby Mode</div>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>',NULL,'[\"http:\\/\\/satkingorbit.test\\/files\\/1\\/pdf\\/5573_SatKing Orbit Brochure Print Version.pdf\"]',NULL,0,'2021-06-26 15:07:17','2021-09-03 17:59:17'),(2,'SatKing 24V to 12V Downconverter','6605','satking-24v-to-12v-downconverter',NULL,'http://satkingorbit.test/photos/1/accessories/6605_SatKing-24V-to-12V-Downconverter (1).jpeg','null',0,'[\"http:\\/\\/satkingorbit.test\\/photos\\/1\\/accessories\\/6605_SatKing-24V-to-12V-Downconverter (1).jpeg\"]',NULL,'<p>Want to use a Satking Orbit on a truck or a bus? Then you will need this 24VDC to 12VDC downconverter. The Orbit just runs on voltages up to 15VDC but some vehicles are configured for 24VDC, if this is the case you will require this device. The unit connect between the power cables of the Orbit and you vehicles power system. Make sure you have 